    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">A fun estimator that turns your dating effort, city size, and how picky you are into a rough timeline for meeting someone new. For entertainment — your real love story is up to you.</p>

    <div class="mb-8"><%= render "shared/ad_slot", slot: "leaderboard" %></div>

